{"tid":1691192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要突破樽頸位，一定要靠閒日朝早嘅行動","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:06:06.000Z","uid":53268,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0abed9e1619d4a682a6f554306aaf254bffc3e3","tid":1691192,"uid":53268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"港共依家仲未跪低其中一個原因係閒日夜晚/weekend搞到點亂都只會影響零售/飲食，其他主要行業影響未算好大。如果朝早有行動(和理非＋勇武)就會令大多人返唔到工，影響大多數行業。<br />\n朝早要夠人一定要提早宣傳，同埋唔可以淨係單靠和理非/勇武是但一邊，一定要兩邊都有行動，目標係癱瘓當日嘅經濟活動。"},{"pid":"31bca222ecd0d6101e0b83d270dcb95115f36b49","tid":1691192,"uid":53268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"朝早運動前一日建議停曬任何行動，令大家可以準備早起"},{"pid":"62254381f2387a6cd752754bce050cc7bdd4f85c","tid":1691192,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4db111cb49a5a267a21ae6638ef8fa61cdf7cf21","tid":1691192,"uid":53268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f2396f98239bb1634de53cd8ed3521f6a72524b","tid":1691192,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42a98c4eba93641e3dd19b934f6f92f763f78664","tid":1691192,"uid":297356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78c4c6fc725cd3bc2db6dc709b574201515bf073","tid":1691192,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bec2cf0a13392f84b361ab1626bcf8d27ee35b4","tid":1691192,"uid":247200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"黎明來到要光復這香港！！<br />\n<br />\n聽朝5點18區開花 &rdquo;千祈唔好&ldquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1694933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\